title: Tahina
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Mediterranean, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Israeli
description: Owner Roy makes home-style Israeli food. Offers pita pockets with falafel, yarakoht (sauteed mushroom), lutsi (fried cauliflower and leek), and sabich (eggplant) among other sides like hummus and potatoes; plus a variety of smoothies.
